34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES03_RiverDiscovery\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Into a new place!\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es03_riverdiscovery.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124998\"\u003eThat is not water, that is sticky tar\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt was Potshot who pressed on into the Blackmire, which is in the northwest of the map, and managed to both find the spire there and solve its puzzle, which he described as the most annoying so far as Keen Games had decided what \u003cem\u003eEnshrouded\u003c/em\u003e needed was more jumping puzzles when they did the area.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHaving saved us from this effort, we were able to fast travel to the spire and glide north to the Sunken Temple… City… whatever.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126045\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126045\" data-attachment-id=\"126045\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_glideintosunkentemple/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2537,1250\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_GlideIntoSunkenTemple\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;On approach to Ancient Sunken City\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_glideintosunkentemple.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126045\"\u003eOn approach to Ancient Sunken City\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe image above is me gliding in after the fact.  My first glide in put me in the buildings to the southwest end of the city where I landed in a bunch of mud.  But mud is safe, even if it slows you down.  It is the tar that is a pain, and that isn’t water the city is in.  That is tar.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126048\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126048\" data-attachment-id=\"126048\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_looktar/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2196,1162\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_LookTar\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Oh hey, tar… yeah\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=1198 1198w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_looktar.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126048\"\u003eOh hey, tar… yeah\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe tar isn’t much to look at.  And it is sticky, like the mud, and will slow you down.  But it has an extra attribute, which is if you stand in it you sink.  And if you are out of stamina and cannot jump, you will sink into it and die.  So there were some issue with that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126047\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126047\" data-attachment-id=\"126047\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_tardeathenaldi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1929,1077\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_TarDeathEnaldi\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Not the first tar death\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_tardeathenaldi.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126047\"\u003eNot the first tar death\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut once we got out of the mud and over the tar to the main building in town, we found a locked door with the usual lights above it indicating that there were some buttons around to press in order to get through it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126051\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126051\" data-attachment-id=\"126051\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_threelights/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2440,1288\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_ThreeLights\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;There are four light!  No, wait, just three…\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_threelights.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126051\"\u003eThere are four light! No, wait, just three…\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt turned out the the Sunken City was a big outdoor puzzle, though the first button wasn’t too tough.  It was literally across the tar within line of sight of the door.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126053\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126053\" data-attachment-id=\"126053\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_firstbutton/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2264,1219\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_FirstButton\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The first button\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_firstbutton.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126053\"\u003eThe first button\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe other buttons were more of a challenge… both more hidden and requiring more jumping, climbing, and for at least one of them, a trampoline jump.  Did I mention the trampolines?  No?  So the devs decided what this area needed, on top of a lot of jumping puzzles, was trampolines.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126056\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126056\" data-attachment-id=\"126056\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_trampoline/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1962,1026\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_Trampoline\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;It just a trampoline Michael…\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_trampoline.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126056\"\u003eIt just a trampoline Michael…\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnshrouded trampolines are a little bouncier than those here on Earth, but once you get the hand of them they will get you places… or bounce you high enough that you can just glide.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnyway, after some searching, a couple of untimely deaths, a bit of fighting, and some trampoline fun, we found all three buttons.  The door was now open.  We would now delve into that area “deep below Sunken Ancient City” mention in the quest, and who could tell what perils that would entail.  Indoor trampolines and cracked skulls maybe?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlas, that part was a bit oversold.  Once the doors were open and we took the stairs down to the basement level, there was just the survivor capsule with the bard in it.  We had found her.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126059\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126059\" data-attachment-id=\"126059\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_bardcapsule/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1602,914\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_BardCapsule\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The survivor capsule was waiting for us\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcapsule.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126059\"\u003eThe survivor capsule was waiting for us\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe opened it up and then had to head back to our base to deploy her… and, of course, find her a bed.  I had to make a new bed for her and our main house is filling up with survivors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOnce the bard was set we were able to open up her crafting options and were rewarded with a selection of interesting options.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126061\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126061\" data-attachment-id=\"126061\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_bardcrafting/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"878,933\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_BardCrafting\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The top bard crafting options\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=376\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=423\" alt=\"\" width=\"423\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=423 423w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=846 846w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=141 141w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=376 376w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_bardcrafting.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126061\"\u003eThe top bard crafting options\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt the top of the list were the medium and large backpack upgrades.  We couldn’t actually make the medium backpack because it required reptile leather, which we had not discovered. (Lots of it in the Blackmire, but we had only just arrived.)  But that was fine, because the large backpack was better and we had all the ingredients for that.  The large added two more rows to our inventory, a welcome addition of space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere were also a bunch of new decorations available, including some pictures to hang.  (Are those Timone and Pumba in the lower right?)  That all boosts the comfort level of our base.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut in the middle were instruments.  I quickly made a flute, which just required a bone, and gave it a try.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126065\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126065\" data-attachment-id=\"126065\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_fluteoutside/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1599,953\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_FluteOutside\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The dog critiquing my style\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_fluteoutside.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126065\"\u003eThe dog critiquing my style\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt turns out, when you put an instrument on your action bar and activate it, you are able to play music.  You are limited to the selection of songs you have found in the world, but that is still pretty neat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMore fun still is that once somebody starts playing, you can join in with them on the song they have chosen, so you can all play together.  And everybody who plays adds to the comfort level of the location.  And the higher the comfort level, the longer your rested buff lasts.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126069\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126069\" data-attachment-id=\"126069\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_musiccomfort/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"589,290\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_MusicComfort\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Three musicians adding +1 to comfort each\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg?w=589\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"589\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg 589w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg?w=150\u0026amp;h=74 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_musiccomfort.jpg?w=500\u0026amp;h=246 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 589px) 100vw, 589px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126069\"\u003eThree musicians adding +1 to comfort each\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt isn’t quite a \u003cem\u003eLOTRO\u003c/em\u003e level experience, where one of my favorite idle tasks it to stand on a corner in Bree and playing selections from They Might Be Giants and The Doors.  But maybe someday there will be a more free-form music system.  The game is still in Early Access after all.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_126070\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-126070\" data-attachment-id=\"126070\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/12/26/the-search-for-music-in-enshrouded/es07_thegroupplays/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1865,978\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES07_TheGroupPlays\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The group playing for an audience\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/es07_thegroupplays-1.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-126070\"\u003eThe group playing for an audience… damn cat is putting his two cents in\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt is a bit odd that you have to sit down to play.  But there are also some ornate instruments recipes out in the world.  Maybe you need those to go professional and play standing up.  We’ll see.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
